{"tid":1835180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府系統性隱瞞肺炎人傳人","createTime":"2020-01-22T17:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T17:49:12.000Z","uid":148013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"894b12b36c5e08a0075ac5105d9d73cae74cf3ac","tid":1835180,"uid":148013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doxKTVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoxKTVF.jpg&h=60260784&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ke8qDnm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKe8qDnm.jpg&h=2d7494c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://engine.scichina.com/publisher/scp/journal/SCLS/doi/10.1007/s11427-020-1637-5?slug=fulltext\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fengine.scichina.com%2Fpublisher%2Fscp%2Fjournal%2FSCLS%2Fdoi%2F10.1007%2Fs11427-020-1637-5%3Fslug%3Dfulltext&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=efdcc977\" target=\"_blank\">http://engine.scichina.com/publisher/scp/journal/SCLS/doi/10.1007/s11427-020-1637-5?slug=fulltext</a><br />\n呢篇野大陸16號投稿，其實果刻已經知佢感染機制&amp;原理係同sars一樣，已經講明極高風險人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但政府喺15號仲講緊「有限度人傳人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECCbyWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECCbyWS.jpg&h=1860ec10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hb3943y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhb3943y.jpg&h=71be8f51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQzEHQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQzEHQe.jpg&h=0b0117c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1KpW07kkUKwr7YKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1KpW07kkUKwr7YKQ&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9e0790cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1KpW07kkUKwr7YKQ</a><br />\n31:15開始睇<br />\n<br />\n而16號都仲官腔記者會話有可能有限度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/01/20200116/20200116_213906_024.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F01%2F20200116%2F20200116_213906_024.html&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=86692e16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/01/20200116/20200116_213906_024.html</a><br />\n<br />\n好大機會係大陸知咗，而香港政府真係唔知/瞞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}